<Base title="Steady — Support" doc>
  <nav><a href="/steady/">← Steady</a></nav>
  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days.</p>

  <h2>Restore your purchase</h2>
  <p>Reinstalled or got a new phone? Open Steady → Settings → <em>Restore Purchase</em>.
     The unlock is tied to your Apple ID, so you'll never pay twice.</p>

  <h2>No readings showing?</h2>
  <p>Steady needs permission to read from Apple Health. Check Settings → Health →
     Data Access &amp; Devices → Steady, then confirm the reading types you want are enabled.</p>

  <h2>Where is my data?</h2>
  <p>On your device, in Apple Health, and in your iCloud account if sync is enabled.
     See the <a href="/steady/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
</Base>
